codex
I verified the cited issues are real. The narrow fixes are: align the top-level JSON-RPC export in source and generated entrypoints, point the benchmark precompile at the actual public precompile surface, publish the CLI shim in `tevm/package.json`, sync the JSR manifest, make `--group=boundary/eip` stop bypassing filtering, and remove shell execution from the two wrappers.
